oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Park City-Lowry School

oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Park City- Lowery (sic.) (Lowry) School, Knoxville, TN. Large group shown in front of school, probably the congregation of the recently burned Bell Ave. Baptist Church, ca. 1912-13. Photo by Thompson, Knoxville.
